found traces of Chang and his mother.

863
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,360
However, they eventually lost them.

864
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,520
It's fine.

865
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,320
Since there were traces,

866
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,320
with the broad connections of the Canal Gang,

867
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,480
they surely will be able to find them.

868
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:38,280
If there's news again,

869
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:41,000
I might leave everything here

870
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,680
and go there to check.

871
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:44,680
You should.

872
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,800
By then,

873
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:46,920
I'll pack your luggage.

874
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:49,880
And then go to Yuqing Monastery

875
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:52,600
to burn you some incense and pray to the gods.

876
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:55,680
ok

877
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:03,840
You talked about inspecting the farmstead earlier.

878
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:06,560
Actually, those farmsteads

879
00:37:06,560 --> 00:37:07,960
don't really earn us a lot of money every year.

880
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,600
You don't need to put too much attention to it.

881
00:37:09,640 --> 00:37:10,760
Don't make yourself too tired.

882
00:37:11,240 --> 00:37:12,640
How could I not to?

883
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,240
Grandmother instructed me

884
00:37:14,720 --> 00:37:15,600
that the assets of the family

885
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:17,320
must be supervised regularly,

886
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:20,080
to prevent those in charge from deceiving us

887
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:20,800
with their reports

888
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,240
and oppressing the people under them.

889
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:24,800
If someone dies because of it,

890
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,200
this is no child's play.

891
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:27,680
So urgent?

892
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:31,280
Why don't I take some time off

893
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:32,280
and go with you?

894
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:33,880
No need.

895
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,425
Just be at ease and stay in the military camp

896
00:37:35,425 --> 00:37:36,080
to train your soldiers.

897
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,800
Just leave a few capable soldiers for me.

898
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:38,800
It will be fine.

899
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,640
Those people in charge of the farmsteads

900
00:37:40,720 --> 00:37:42,480
are not really killing and looting bandits.

901
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:43,520
They are capable enough.

902
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:56,040
If I leave everything behind here

903
00:37:56,160 --> 00:37:58,240
and go look for Chang alone,

904
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,600
Will you be unhappy?

905
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:05,160
In the past, Nanny Chang asked me too.

906
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,360
I don't know

907
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,600
why I should be unhappy.

908
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:10,160
I think that,

909
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:11,720
in the next life,

910
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,320
I will want to be your child too.

911
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,040
Marrying you

912
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,240
is really good karma

913
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,800
that I've accumulated from saving humankind

914
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,240
in the my previous several reincarnations.

915
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:41,800
You already told me this.

916
00:38:42,240 --> 00:38:43,320
I know.

917
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:46,320
Alright, take a bath now.

918
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,400
Don't let the water get cold.

919
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:49,040
Let me get you some cloths.

920
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,200
What should I do

921
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,960
to make you trust me?

922
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:10,440
Why are you so late?

923
00:39:10,680 --> 00:39:11,960
Old Commander Bo is waiting for you.

924
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:13,720
What happened?

925
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:15,000
Did my army

926
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:15,760
fight with other people again?

927
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,400
No.

928
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,240
His Majesty made an edict yesterday

929
00:39:18,520 --> 00:39:19,925
that he will inspect the training of the army

930
00:39:19,925 --> 00:39:20,560
the next few days.

931
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:22,200
The two old generals

932
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,560
went to inform all the different military camps

933
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,960
to organize and prepare.

934
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:28,600
Inspection?

935
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,640
With such a big thing,

936
00:39:30,640 --> 00:39:32,000
how come there were no news from Prince Huan?

937
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:33,440
Who knows.

938
00:39:35,560 --> 00:39:37,240
I wanted to take a few days off

939
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:38,800
to settle some personal matters

940
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:39,600
in my family.

941
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:40,800
Better not to bring that up anymore.

942
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:41,840
This is serious matter.

943
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:42,680
It can't be handled sloppily.

944
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:44,040
Can't you see that even Emperor's Uncle is here?

945
00:40:30,480 --> 00:40:32,080
I, Ba Fu,

946
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:34,120
greets Big Madam.

947
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:36,320
Big Madam, welcome.

948
00:40:37,720 --> 00:40:38,640
The house

949
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:40,480
has been prepared.

950
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,880
Manager Ba, you have worked hard.

951
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:45,760
It's getting dark soon

952
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:47,200
and I still made you wait here.

953
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:49,920
Big Madam is a noble person.

954
00:40:50,720 --> 00:40:51,280
Having some time to spare

955
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,320
in coming here to visit us

956
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,680
is our good fortune.

957
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:56,200
We are eager to greet you.

958
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:58,040
Thank you, Manager Ba.

959
00:40:58,720 --> 00:41:00,040
Everyone, you all are tired too.

960
00:41:00,080 --> 00:41:01,240
Just go home and rest now.

961
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:03,560
I'll check the accounting books tomorrow.

962
00:41:03,680 --> 00:41:04,520
This...

963
00:41:04,720 --> 00:41:06,000
Go now. I'm tired.

964
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:09,240
Thank you for understanding, Big Madam.

965
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:19,840
This Heishan Farmstead

966
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,080
and the Guyan Farmstead behind

967
00:41:21,080 --> 00:41:22,320
can't compare to the Xiaoyu Farmstead

968
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:23,200
I brought as my dowry.

969
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:25,440
This is a penal farm set up by the government.

970
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,400
We're also not familiar with the people here.

971
00:41:26,680 --> 00:41:28,840
Sister Cuiwei, I'm a bit scared.

972
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:31,040
Silly girl.

973
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:32,560
Have you prepared all the items

974
00:41:32,560 --> 00:41:33,480
that Big Madam

975
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:34,440
asked?

976
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:35,480
all set

977
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,560
there

978
00:41:41,680 --> 00:41:43,520
She indeed was from a scholarly family.

979
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:44,800
Such bearing.

980
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,440
No matter how imposing her bearing is,

981
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,720
she's still just a young Madam.

982
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,400
What can she know?

983
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:56,720
Tomorrow just report everything

984
00:41:56,720 --> 00:41:58,000
according to what we discussed.

985
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:02,440
It's just the newly-wed wife

986
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:05,240
wants to come out

987
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:06,320
to visit her fields and show off her might.

988
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:07,800
Just let her show off.

989
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:10,600
This will be over after some coaxing.
